Source: pdiplugin-decl-netcdf
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Julien Bigot <julien.bigot@cea.fr>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 11),
  cmake (>= 3.10),
  libgmock-dev (>= 1.8) <!bionic !nocheck>,
  libgtest-dev (>= 1.8) <!bionic !nocheck>,
  libnetcdf-dev (>= 4.6.0),
  libnetcdf-mpi-dev (>= 4.6.0) <!bionic>,
  libpdi-dev,
  mpi-default-dev,
  mpich <!nocheck>,
  openmpi-bin <!nocheck>,
  pdiplugin-mpi-mpich <!nocheck>,
  pdiplugin-mpi-openmpi <!nocheck>,
